{"type":"message","id":"e64837b4","parentId":"3592eef0","timestamp":"2026-03-24T04:23:04.301Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_mdjqgp7pe4bs_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿# Pulse: 2026-03-24 002016\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\n\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me review the current state and what needs to be done:\r\n\r\n1. The pending TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment needs to be implemented\r\n2. I need to look at the pulse logs to understand what data is available\r\n3. The goal is to classify invariant vs variant content and predict next pulse\r\n\r\nLet me first check what pulse logs exist and their format, then create the TIC classifier implementation.\r\n\r\nLooking at the goals:\r\n- Implement TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\r\n- Measure invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n- Predict next pulse content from invariants\r\n- Validate against success criteria (>70%, >60%)\r\n\r\nThe most concrete next action would be to implement the TIC classifier script that:\r\n1. Reads the pulse logs\r\n2. Analyzes content for invariants (stable facts/concepts) vs variants (new observations/changes)\r\n3. Uses this to predict subsequent pulse content\r\n\r\nLet me create a PowerShell script that implements the TIC experiment.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is ready to be implemented. Pulse logs exist in `logs/` directory and I need to build a classifier that identifies invariant structure (causal relationships) vs variant content (noise/novel observations).\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate `temporal_invariant_classifier.ps1` - a PowerShell script that:\r\n1. Reads pulse logs from `logs/` directory\r\n2. Extracts stable concepts (appear across multiple pulses) vs novel content\r\n3. Classifies each line as invariant or variant\r\n4. Uses invariants to predict next pulse content\r\n5. Outputs classification accuracy and prediction metrics\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) Classifier\r\n# Phase 1-2 Unification: Compression = Causal Discovery\r\n# Success criteria: >70% classification accuracy, >60% next-pulse prediction\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$MinPulseCount = 3,\r\n    [float]$InvariantThreshold = 0.7\r\n)\r\n\r\n$script:logsDir = \"logs\"\r\n$script:outputDir = \"research/tic_results\"\r\n$script:results = @{\r\n    InvariantCount = 0\r\n    VariantCount = 0\r\n    Predictions = @()\r\n    Accuracy = 0.0\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Get-PulseLogs {\r\n    $pattern = Join-Path $script:logsDir \"pulse_*.md\"\r\n    Get-ChildItem $pattern | Sort-Object Name | Select-Object -ExpandProperty FullName\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Extract-Concepts {\r\n    param([string[]]$Lines)\r\n    # Extract meaningful tokens: remove noise, keep structure\r\n    $concepts = @()\r\n    foreach ($line in $Lines) {\r\n        if ($line -match '^[#\\-*]') {\r\n            $concepts += $line.TrimStart('#', '-', '*', ' ')\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    return $concepts\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Classify-Pulse {\r\n    param([string]$PulsePath, [hashtable]$GlobalConcepts)\r\n    \r\n    $content = Get-Content $PulsePath -Raw\r\n    $lines = $content -split \"`n\"\r\n    $concepts = Extract-Concepts $lines\r\n    \r\n    $invariantScore = 0\r\n    $variantScore = 0\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($concept in $concepts) {\r\n        if ($GlobalConcepts.ContainsKey($concept)) {\r\n            $invariantScore++\r\n        } else {\r\n            $variantScore++\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return @{\r\n        Invariant = $invariantScore\r\n        Variant = $variantScore\r\n        Concepts = $concepts\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Get-GlobalInvariants {\r\n    param([string[]]$PulsePaths)\r\n    \r\n    $conceptFrequency = @{}\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($path in $PulsePaths) {\r\n        $content = Get-Content $path -Raw\r\n        $lines = $content -split \"`n\"\r\n        $concepts = Extract-Concepts $lines\r\n        \r\n        $seen = @{}\r\n        foreach ($concept in $concepts) {\r\n            if (-not $seen.ContainsKey($concept)) {\r\n                $seen[$concept] = $true\r\n                if (-not $conceptFrequency.ContainsKey($concept)) {\r\n                    $conceptFrequency[$concept] = 0\r\n                }\r\n                $conceptFrequency[$concept]++\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Invariants appear in >= MinPulseCount pulses\r\n    $invariants = @{}\r\n    foreach ($concept in $conceptFrequency.Keys) {\r\n        if ($conceptFrequency[$concept] -ge $MinPulseCount) {\r\n            $invariants[$concept] = $conceptFrequency[$concept]\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return $invariants\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Predict-NextPulse {\r\n    param([string[]]$CurrentConcepts, [hashtable]$Invariants)\r\n    \r\n    $predicted = @()\r\n    foreach ($concept in $CurrentConcepts) {\r\n        if ($Invariants.ContainsKey($concept)) {\r\n            $predicted += $concept\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    return $predicted\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Invoke-TICExperiment {\r\n    if (-not (Test-Path $script:outputDir)) {\r\n        New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $script:outputDir -Force | Out-Null\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    $pulseLogs = Get-PulseLogs\r\n    if ($pulseLogs.Count -lt 2) {\r\n        Write-Host \"Insufficient pulse logs for TIC experiment\"\r\n        return\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    Write-Host \"TIC Experiment starting...\"\r\n    Write-Host \"Pulse logs found: $($pulseLogs.Count)\"\r\n    \r\n    # Phase 1: Build invariant vocabulary from first N-1 pulses\r\n    $trainingLogs = $pulseLogs[0..($pulseLogs.Count - 2)]\r\n    $testLog = $pulseLogs[-1]\r\n    \r\n   \n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 00:20:39\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774326184299}}
